## Known Bug Regression Tests

All nine original bugs are resolved. Regression tests to keep passing:

### BUG-2 (similarity score — resolved)
```rust
#[test]
fn test_similarity_bounded() {
    // 1.0 / (1.0 + distance) is always in (0, 1] regardless of distance magnitude
    for distance in [0.0f32, 0.5, 1.0, 10.0, 1000.0] {
        let sim = 1.0 / (1.0 + distance);
        assert!(sim > 0.0 && sim <= 1.0, "similarity out of bounds for distance {distance}");
    }
}
```

### BUG-6 (import deduplication — resolved)
```rust
#[tokio::test]
async fn test_import_dedup() {
    let tmp = TempDir::new().unwrap();
    let graph = KnowledgeGraph::new(tmp.path()).unwrap();
    let mut ingestion = DataIngestion::new(&graph);

    // Import the same file twice
    ingestion.import_json_data("./defaults/data/memory.json").await.unwrap();
    let count_after_first = graph.get_stats().unwrap().node_count;

    ingestion.import_json_data("./defaults/data/memory.json").await.unwrap();
    let count_after_second = graph.get_stats().unwrap().node_count;

    assert_eq!(count_after_first, count_after_second, "Re-import must not create duplicates");
}
```

